    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists just want to talk to a person, but there isn't one. you can't fix a shell if the thing inside it is already gone. it feels like if i died tomorrow, it wouldnt even be a loss, because there's nobody left to lose. it's just... empty. it's like the movie has finally reached the end credits but the screen is just black.",
