    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "stepping out of the theater... that's exactly it. but i'm scared that even if i leave, the dark just follows me. or that there's no 'outside' to go to. if i just stopped everything, would it actually be peaceful? or is it just more of the same nothingness?",
